data.description: Take a look at this home, tucked away on a cul-de-sac road, away from the busy roads.  This home features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guest. The kitchen has granite counter tops, and gas oven range. In the master bedroom, you’ll find tall barrels ceilings and walk in shower, jet tub and walk in closet in the bath. The 5th (optional) bedroom being upstairs, it also makes a great spot for a home theater set up. The driveway has been extended, into the backyard, with gate access for storing trailers, mowers or anything else you’d need parked/stored. Roof was replaced in 2021 with impact resistant shingle and home is equipped with tankless water heater, so you'll never have to cut those showers short!
